block content 
  article.grid-container.portfolio-intro
    div

      
      h1  Hey, Potential Employers

      
      p.lead.text-light
        | This portfolio demonstrate my myraid skills, including but not limited to web development, soft skills, life long learning, techincal savyy, and team player! Am I hired? 
  article.grid-container.portfolio-index
    
    .grid-x.grid-margin-x.small-up-2.medium-up-2.large-up-3
      
        
      
      each val in data
        .cell
          a(href=`/project/${val.id}`)
